OL,6,FThe BBC will not appeal over Gerry
OL,7,FAdams' defamation victory against the
OL,8,Forganisation.
OL,10,FMr Adams, a former president of Sinn
OL,11,FFein, said there needed to be
OL,12,F"substantial reform" of the
OL,13,Fbroadcaster.
OL,15,FMr Adams took the BBC to court over a
OL,16,F2016 episode of its Spotlight
OL,17,Fprogramme, and an accompanying online
OL,18,Fstory, which he said defamed him.
