OL,3,CBBC will not appeal Adams' defamation
OL,4,Ccase win
OL,6,FLast month, a jury at the High Court
OL,7,Fin Dublin found in his favour and
OL,8,Fawarded him #84,000.
OL,10,FThe BBC, which was found by the jury
OL,11,Fnot to have acted in good faith nor in
OL,12,Fa fair and reasonable way, was also
OL,13,Fordered to pay the former Sinn Fein
OL,14,Fleader's legal costs.
OL,16,FAfter the decision, the broadcaster's
OL,17,Flegal team was granted a stay in the
OL,18,Fpayment of the full award as it took
OL,19,Ftime to consider an appeal.
