OL,3,CBBC will not appeal Adams' defamation
OL,4,Ccase win
OL,6,FHowever, on Friday, the BBC confirmed
OL,7,Fit would not pursue an appeal.
OL,9,FA spokesperson said: "We have given
OL,10,Fcareful consideration to the jury's
OL,11,Fdecision.
OL,13,F"We will not be appealing its verdict,
OL,14,Fbringing this matter to a conclusion.
OL,16,F"We remain committed to public
OL,17,Finterest journalism and to serving all
OL,18,FBBC audiences."
