OL,3,CBBC will not appeal Adams' defamation
OL,4,Ccase win
OL,6,FIn a statement issued through the Sinn
OL,7,FFein press office on Friday, Mr Adams
OL,8,Fsaid: "The decision not to appeal by
OL,9,Fthe British Broadcasting Corporation
OL,10,Fhas to be followed by a substantial
OL,11,Freform of its internal journalistic
OL,12,Fprocesses and a recognition that it
OL,13,Fcannot continue to be a voice for the
OL,14,FBritish state in Ireland.
OL,16,F"It must also become more accountable
OL,17,Fto the public.
