OL,6,F"The Dublin Court found the BBC guilty
OL,7,Fof libel and rejected its claim that
OL,8,Fits journalism was fair and reasonable
OL,9,Fand in the public interest.
OL,11,F"The British Broadcasting Corporation
OL,12,Fis a public service provider. There is
OL,13,Fan onus on the BBC to ensure that in
OL,14,Fthe future its ethics and journalism
OL,15,Freflect the principles and values of a
OL,16,Fpublic broadcast service.
OL,18,F"As I have already said the damages
OL,19,Fwill be donated to good causes."
